  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Nine novellas drawn from the months after the Dropsite Massacre at Isstvan V, each visiting a different corner of the new war. Graham McNeill puts Roboute Guilliman's officers through a training scenario that already smells like the disaster waiting at Calth; James Swallow watches a single agitator unravel a peaceful Ultima Segmentum world; Nick Kyme sends Salamander and Ultramarine envoys on a diplomatic errand; John French interrogates the last Remembrancer in Imperial custody; Chris Wraight follows Thousand Sons survivors fleeing burning Prospero; Gav Thorpe joins Raven Guard and Iron Hands picking their way out of the slaughter; Dan Abnett rides with Little Horus Aximand; Rob Sanders garrisons the loyalist Iron Warrior Barabas Dantioch at Hydra Cordatus; and Aaron Dembski-Bowden brokers a black parley between the Lion and Konrad Curze.",
